<TR><TH>About RecruitFree.com</TH></TR>
<TR><TD>
RecruitFree.com is a completely free recruitment site.  The site allows employers to advertise their jobs for free and for job-seekers to find jobs quickly and easily.
<P>
<B>For job-seekers</B><BR>
If you're looking for a job then RecruitFree.com provides you with an easy-to-use database of vacancies that you can search through. With 398 vacancies currently in the database there's plenty of choice! Applying for jobs is very easy - just contact the employer directly!  Since RecruitFree does not make any money from introducing candidates to employers there's no need for us to act as the "middle-man".
<P>
<B>For employers</B><BR>
The fact that RecruitFree.com is free means that any employer can advertise their vacancies quickly and easily without the need to register.  Just type in the details of your first vacancy, and it will be live immediately in the database.
<P>
Once you have entered your first vacancy you will be allocated a password so you can update the details of the vacancy, add new vacancies, and remove vacancies once positions have been filled.
<P>
<B>What's the catch?</B><BR>
There's no catch!  The service is free and there are no obligations. Your details will not be passed on to any other organisations so you don't need to worry about being bombarded with loads more junk mail!
<P>
<B>Why was RecruitFree.com developed?</B><BR>
RecruitFree.com was developed to provide an easy and free way for employers to advertise their vacancies and for job seekers to have the best choice of available vacancies.
<P>
<B>Your views</B><BR>
RecruitFree.com was developed to serve job-seekers and employers.  If you have any comments or ideas on how the site could be improved please let us know by emailing us at <A HREF="mailto:theteam@recruitfree.com">TheTeam@RecruitFree.com</A>. 
